Package: peach-dyndns-host
Architecture: any
Depends:
  ${misc:Depends}
  , peach-base
  , bind9
  , dnsutils
  , nginx
  , python3
  , python3-aiohttp
Description: HTTP(S)-based dynamic DNS updater server.
  Provides dyndns.org-like service that accepts update requests
  via HTTP(S) and forwards them to a locally running
  DNS server via nsupdate -l. Works with most routers.
  Readme: https://github.com/SFTtech/sftdyn/blob/master/README.md
